e Alpensinfonie，Don Juan，Eine Heldenleben都係巨匠之作。基本上佢嘅作品見證住德奧音樂衰落"},{"pid":"432c475f81c2d7125ae8c196ef568ef4328875b8","tid":857939,"uid":357680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43bad4142117e9e902d203e242944545f313b17e","tid":857939,"uid":94711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T12:21:54.000Z","msg":"近排聽Campanella 上癮<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lWaOnqmtr9U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlWaOnqmtr9U&d=diPzZA6xL86YPXKEDuBT8KNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=8944c26f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lWaOnqmtr9U</a><br />\n條友拉琴勁到痴線<br />\n<br />\n想知除左Vivaldi - 4 season <br />\nCannon in D <br />\n仲有冇好聽/易入耳既古典音樂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T18:20:49.000Z","msg":"我有一個Youtube Channel，每星期上載新影片，也分享一些關於音樂家的小知識。可去看看<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n頻道名稱: Roseyam KY<br />\n最新影片: <a href=\"https://youtu.be/r6oBORdWfvY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fr6oBORdWfvY&d=diPzZA6xL86YPXKEDuBT8KNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=052ca28b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/r6oBORdWfvY</a>"}]}